de.systemagmbh.tools.logger.checker
Class CSysCheckerByLevelCombination

java.lang.Object
  de.systemagmbh.tools.logger.checker.ASysLogChecker
      de.systemagmbh.tools.logger.checker.CSysCheckerByLevelCombination
All Implemented Interfaces:
ISysComponent, ISysDevelopmentLogSwitch, ISysGlobal, ISysLogChecker, ISysLogConstants
public class CSysCheckerByLevelCombination
extends ASysLogChecker
implements ISysLogConstants

The class CSysCheckerByLevelCombination is used for checking loglevels. These levels have to be defined in the new configuration style setting levels as coma separated list of the following values:
FATAL, ERROR, WARNING, ALWAYS, COM, STEP, INFO, METHOD, ALL

Version:
$Revision: 1.1 $
Author:
Udo Friedrich, Torsten Knauft
